item.title: Women in Technology Galway meetup-February 2016
item.description: Thank youto everyone who joined us tonight. A special thanks to our speaker Edel Browne. Edel is an excellent STEM role model. The community is lucky to have this young inspirational lady. To find out more about the innovative device designed by Edel, see Free Feet Medical or follow Edel on Twitter @EdelBrownie. <img src=”/img/edel.jpg” style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;width="400” height="300"> Thank you to our hosts Annie, Maireadand Tracyfrom Workbench Galway for setting up the space and refreshments.
